1.2
log
@Correct eisa i/o ports layout structure, this has probably been broken
when switching from gcc 2.95, if not forever.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: mongoosereg.h,v 1.1 2004/10/29 20:23:37 miod Exp $	*/

